    AF3: Version Reset: Rollback project description to a previous saved state.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Exceptions:</th><td>
    E1: Modification Locked: System prevents editing once a contract is signed.<br>
    E2: Negative Budget: System rejects any budget update below $0.<br>
    E3: Conflict: Broker submits a proposal while client is editing title.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Priority:</th><td>Medium</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Business Rules:</th><td>
    BR-37: Budget modifications exceeding 20% will invalidate all current broker bids.<br>
    BR-38: Cancellation is only allowed if no broker has been officially hired.<br>
    BR-39: Core technical stack tags cannot be removed if they are already in specs.
  </td></tr>
</table>

