  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Priority:</th><td>High</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Business Rules:</th><td>
    BR-40: Approved specs act as the technical annex to the project contract.<br>
    BR-41: Milestones must be clearly defined with at least 3 acceptance criteria each.<br>
    BR-42: Spec approval is a one-way transition; reverting requires admin reset.
  </td></tr>
</table>

