    AF2: Evidence Filter: Categorize viewable files by 'My Evidence' vs 'Other side'.<br>
    AF3: Timeline Toggle: Switch between 'Compact' and 'Full Detail' event views.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Exceptions:</th><td>
    E1: Forbidden Access: Attempting to view a dispute for a project the user doesn't own.<br>
    E2: Loading Error: Encrypted evidence files fail to decrypt for preview.<br>
    E3: Deleted Item: Admin has removed a specific comment for violating community guidelines.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Priority:</th><td>Medium</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Business Rules:</th><td>
    BR-70: Internal admin notes are never visible to clients or defendants.<br>
    BR-71: Dispute information is retained for 7 years as per financial compliance laws.<br>
    BR-72: Real-time status sync is required for all active viewers of the case details.
  </td></tr>
</table>

