    PRE1: Actor is a verified member of the project or has an active invitation.<br>
    PRE2: Real-time messaging service is online.<br>
    PRE3: User has not been silenced or banned from the specific channel.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Postconditions:</th><td>
    POST1: User's online status is broadcasted to other participants.<br>
    POST2: Last 50 messages are loaded into the chat window.<br>
    POST3: Push notifications are silenced for the active session.
  </td></tr>
