  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Exceptions:</th><td>
    E1: Transaction Declined: Bank or Gateway rejects the charge; plan remains unchanged.<br>
    E2: Feature Conflict: Downgrade blocked if the provider has more active projects than the lower tier allows.<br>
