  <tr><th>Business Rules:</th><td>
    BR-115: Premium subscriptions are non-refundable once the provider applies to a job using premium benefits.<br>
    BR-116: Visibility boost in 'Talent Search' is proportional to the subscription tier level.<br>
    BR-117: Agency plans allow adding up to 10 sub-accounts under one primary billing.
  </td></tr>
</table>

