  <tr><th>Preconditions:</th><td>
    PRE1: User has sufficient 'Application Credits' or an active subscription.<br>
    PRE2: Profile completion is above 80% (System requirement for high-level jobs).<br>
    PRE3: Project is currently in 'Hiring' status.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Postconditions:</th><td>
