  <tr><th class="header-cell">ID and Name:</th><td class="header-cell"><b>UC-44 — Manage Project Milestone (Freelancer)</b></td></tr>
  <tr><th>Created By:</th><td>AnNPCE</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Date Created:</th><td>15/01/2026</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Primary Actor:</th><td>Freelancer</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Secondary Actors:</th><td>System, Lead Broker</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Description:</th><td>Update progress on assigned technical milestones and submit deliverables for internal review.</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Trigger:</th><td>Freelancer selects their current task from the 'Work' board.</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Preconditions:</th><td>
    PRE1: Freelancer is assigned to a specific milestone by the Broker.<br>
    PRE2: Project is 'IN_PROGRESS'.<br>
    PRE3: Milestone is unlocked for work.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Postconditions:</th><td>
    POST1: Milestone status changes to 'INTERNAL_REVIEW' or 'READY_FOR_CLIENT'.<br>
    POST2: Broker is notified to verify the uploaded code/files.<br>
    POST3: Progress metrics (velocity) are updated in the team analytics.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Normal Flow:</th><td>
    1. Update task completion percentage.<br>
    2. Link to Git repository or upload zip file.<br>
    3. Add technical notes about the implementation.<br>
    4. Mark as 'Ready for Broker'.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Alternative Flows:</th><td>
    AF1: Request Block Removal: Flag a milestone as 'Blocked' and notify the team.<br>
    AF2: Split Task: Break a sub-task into smaller atomic units for better tracking.<br>
    AF3: Postpone Task: Request a 1-2 day delay for a specific technical deliverable.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Exceptions:</th><td>
    E1: Permission Denied: Attempting to update a milestone assigned to another freelancer.<br>
    E2: Repo Sync Error: System cannot pull from the linked external repository.<br>
    E3: Required File Missing: marked 'Ready' without any attached deliverables.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Priority:</th><td>High</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Business Rules:</th><td>
    BR-124: Freelancers cannot mark a milestone as 'Delivered' to the client directly; it must pass the Broker first.<br>
    BR-125: All code submissions must include a brief description of changes (Changelog).<br>
    BR-126: Milestone progress updates must be made at least once every 48 hours for active projects.
  </td></tr>
</table>

