<table>
  <tr><th class="header-cell">ID and Name:</th><td class="header-cell"><b>UC-45 — Feedback Project Milestone</b></td></tr>
  <tr><th>Created By:</th><td>AnNPCE</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Date Created:</th><td>15/01/2026</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Primary Actor:</th><td>Freelancer</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Secondary Actors:</th><td>Broker, System</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Description:</th><td>Provide technical input or request clarifications on milestone requirements.</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Trigger:</th><td>Freelancer views a milestone detail card.</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Preconditions:</th><td>
    PRE1: User is an active member of the project team.<br>
    PRE2: Milestone status is not 'Completed'.<br>
    PRE3: Chat or comment section is enabled for the project.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Postconditions:</th><td>
    POST1: Feedback comment is saved and timestamped.<br>
    POST2: Notification is sent to the assigned Broker/Manager.<br>
    POST3: The feedback is archived in the milestone history for future reference.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Normal Flow:</th><td>
    1. Select a milestone.<br>
    2. Post a technical clarification or suggestion.<br>
    3. Tag the relevant Broker for a response.<br>
    4. View the thread of previous comments.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Alternative Flows:</th><td>
    AF1: Resolve Feedback: Mark a previous question as closed once answered.<br>
    AF2: Private Team Comment: Leave a technical note hidden from the client.<br>
    AF3: Upvote Suggestion: Team members agree with a specific feedback item.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Exceptions:</th><td>
    E1: Locked Thread: No further comments allowed after milestone is finalized.<br>
    E2: User Muted: Freelancer is blocked from posting due to previous community violations.<br>
    E3: Attachment Fail: Trying to attach a code snippet that exceeds the line limit.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Priority:</th><td>Medium</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Business Rules:</th><td>
    BR-127: Feedback for technical obstacles must be categorized as 'Blocker' or 'Info'.<br>
    BR-128: Brokers must acknowledge 'Blocker' feedback within 24 hours.<br>
    BR-129: All technical feedback is accessible to the client unless marked as 'Internal'.
  </td></tr>
</table>

