  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Priority:</th><td>High</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Business Rules:</th><td>
    BR-130: The 'Approved' spec is the only legally binding technical reference for disputes.<br>
    BR-131: Spec views by freelancers are tracked to ensure everyone is on the same version.<br>
    BR-132: Freelancers have Read-Only access to the official project specification.
  </td></tr>
</table>

