<table>
  <tr><th class="header-cell">ID and Name:</th><td class="header-cell"><b>UC-47 — Feedback Project Specs</b></td></tr>
  <tr><th>Created By:</th><td>AnNPCE</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Date Created:</th><td>15/01/2026</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Primary Actor:</th><td>Freelancer</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Secondary Actors:</th><td>Broker, Client</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Description:</th><td>Flag technical issues or propose improvements to the project requirements.</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Trigger:</th><td>Freelancer highlights a section of the spec or clicks "Propose Change".</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Preconditions:</th><td>
    PRE1: Freelancer is a member of the project team.<br>
    PRE2: Spec is in an 'Editable' phase (Phase 2 or early Phase 3).<br>
    PRE3: User has found a technical inconsistency or efficiency improvement.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Postconditions:</th><td>
    POST1: Feedback note is pinned to the specific requirement line/item.<br>
    POST2: System alerts the Broker to a potential technical adjustment.<br>
    POST3: Recommendation is logged for the final spec review meeting.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Normal Flow:</th><td>
    1. Highlight a specific requirement.<br>
    2. Suggest a technical alternative or flag an impossibility.<br>
    3. Provide reasoning/justification.<br>
    4. Submit suggestion.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Alternative Flows:</th><td>
    AF1: Retract Feedback: Remove a suggestion before it is reviewed by the Broker.<br>
    AF2: Vote on Proposal: Team members support a specific technical change.<br>
    AF3: Post Design Reference: Attach a screenshot to explain the feedback better.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Exceptions:</th><td>
    E1: Spec Frozen: Attempting to feedback on a document that is already frozen for billing.<br>
    E2: Overlapping Suggestion: Another team member has already flagged the same issue.<br>
    E3: Excessive Feedback: Limit of 50 feedback items per freelancer per spec version.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Priority:</th><td>Medium</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Business Rules:</th><td>
    BR-133: Freelancer feedback is advisory and must be approved by the Broker before updating the spec.<br>
    BR-134: Suggestions that change the project scope are automatically highlighted in RED.<br>
    BR-135: Feedback must be linked to a specific requirement ID (e.g., REQ-101).
  </td></tr>
</table>

<!-- UC-48 -->
<table>
  <tr><th class="header-cell">ID and Name:</th><td class="header-cell"><b>UC-48 — Rate Client/Broker</b></td></tr>
  <tr><th>Created By:</th><td>AnNPCE</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Date Created:</th><td>15/01/2026</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Primary Actor:</th><td>Freelancer</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Secondary Actors:</th><td>System</td></tr>
  <tr><th>Description:</th><td>Evaluate the leadership and professionalism of the Client and Broker post-project.</td></tr>
