  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Normal Flow:</th><td>
    1. Select project.<br>
    2. Rate Client (Clarity, Payment speed).<br>
    3. Rate Broker (Management, Tech Support).<br>
    4. Submit final evaluation.
  </td></tr>
  <tr><th>Alternative Flows:</th><td>
    AF1: Anonymous Review: Submit feedback without showing the freelancer's name (internal only).<br>
